Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Statements

    2 Statements: Statement Statements
    3           | Statement
    4           | /* empty */

    5 Statement: DeclStat
    6          | ExprStat
    7          | IfStat
    8          | ForStat
    9          | WhileStat
   10          | RetStat
   11          | PrintStat
   12          | Block
   13          | MethodDef
   14          | ClassDef
   15          | Expr
   16          | error Smicln
   17          | error Clspar

   18 ClassDef: Class Id Block

   19 MethodDef: Modifiers Type Id Opnbr Params Clsbr Block
   20          | Modifiers Type Id Opnbr Params Clsbr Smicln

   21 Modifiers: Modifiers Modifier
   22          | Modifier
   23          | /* empty */

   24 Modifier: Public
   25         | StaticStat
   26         | Func_type

   27 Type: Datatype
   28     | Void
   29     | Id

   30 Params: ParamList
   31       | /* empty */

   32 ParamList: Param
   33          | ParamList Comma Param

   34 Param: Type Id
   35      | Type Id Osqbr Clsqbr

   36 Block: Opnpar Statements Clspar

   37 DeclStat: Type Id Assign Expr Smicln
   38         | Type Id Smicln
   39         | Type Id Osqbr Const1 Clsqbr Assign Opnpar ArrayVals Clspar Smicln
   40         | Type Id Osqbr Clsqbr Assign Opnpar ArrayVals Clspar Smicln
   41         | Type Id Assign New Id Opnbr Clsbr Smicln
   42         | Declare Type Id Smicln
   43         | Type Id Assign Opnbr Type Clsbr Expr Smicln

   44 ArrayVals: Expr
   45          | ArrayVals Comma Expr
   46          | /* empty */

   47 ExprStat: Expr Assign Expr Smicln
   48         | Expr Smicln
   49         | Id Assign Expr '+' Smicln

   50 IfStat: If Opnbr Expr Clsbr Statement
   51       | If Opnbr Expr Clsbr Statement Else Statement
   52       | If Opnbr Expr Clsbr
   53       | If Expr

   54 ForStat: For Opnbr ForInit Smicln Expr Smicln Expr Clsbr Statement
   55        | For Opnbr ForInit Smicln Expr Smicln Expr Clsbr

   56 ForInit: Type Id Assign Expr
   57        | Expr Assign Expr
   58        | /* empty */

   59 WhileStat: While Opnbr Expr Clsbr Statement
   60          | While Opnbr Expr Clsbr

   61 RetStat: Ret Expr Smicln
   62        | Ret Smicln

   63 PrintStat: Print Opnbr PrintArgs Clsbr Smicln
   64          | Print Opnbr Smicln Clsbr

   65 PrintArgs: Expr
   66          | PrintArgs Comma Expr
   67          | /* empty */

   68 Expr: Expr '+' Expr
   69     | Expr '-' Expr
   70     | Expr '*' Expr
   71     | Expr '/' Expr
   72     | Expr Relop Expr
   73     | Expr Logicop Expr
   74     | Logicop Expr
